{"tid":145065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【777萬撐警】蕭定一捐20萬：七警屋企人好可憐","createTime":"2017-03-06T03:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T12:23:08.000Z","uid":18348,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c144e62425eecbf46dcac56343c606dac391a920","tid":145065,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170305/large/1488710164_2b77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F1488710164_2b77.jpg&h=37d0452f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lsfxw5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lsfxw5&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=1a0e4f54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lsfxw5</a> ），支持七警嘅，仲有一班香港影視娛樂同業。向太陳嵐今日代表一班同業，捐出7,777,777港元俾「敬言仁」基金，呢一大筆捐款，有唔少娛圈猛人出錢，包括周焯華、向華強、「六嬸」方逸華各捐出100萬；楊受成、林小明各捐50萬；之前表明撐警嘅曾志偉，就捐咗20萬。<br />\n<br />\n呢777萬入面，HMV數碼中國聯席主席的蕭定一都有份，捐出20萬支持警察，佢今日回應《蘋果》時話：「向太（陳嵐）發起所有娛樂公司一齊籌款，籌錢畀佢哋（七警）屋企人，雖然七警有罪，但佢哋啲屋企人係無罪，我覺得佢哋屋企人好可憐，我就略表心意。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170305/56388703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170305%2F56388703&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=e14af7c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170305%2F56388703&h=b3ac1ada\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170305/56388703</a>"},{"pid":"2eb76b49387bb9e47a72a9d47f17233c996f35fd","tid":145065,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"燒生好野"},{"pid":"5eb82b9dbb6423def2d5f5adfe384bec8e47a4a6","tid":145065,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山"},{"pid":"4cd879d